fields.name: New wholesale prices, subsidy free CFDs, separate negs for tidal
fields.description: No Excel quirks, new wholesale prices, no policies, separate negotiations for tidal lagoon, subsidy free CFDs only from 2026. NB Have adjusted up strike price of OFW in 2030 from 94.69 to 95 to be equal to gas price (otherwise 9.498GW of OFW was being deployed in 2030) Have adjusted down the number of new TL projects available, as the number in the Excel sheet seemed unrealistic (a new one every year from 2025 to 2030) - if they are having separate negotiations they'll all get built.
